Source: dsme
Section: misc
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ismo Laitinen <ismo.laitinen@nokia.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 4.1.0)
Standards-Version: 3.6.1

Package: dsme
Section: misc
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: Device State Management Entity
 This package contains the Device State Management Entity which provides state 
 management features such as service monitoring, process watchdog and 
 inactivity tracking.

Package: libdsme0
Section: libs
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: DSME dsmesock dynamic library
 This package contains dynamic libraries for programs that communicate with the
 Device State Management Entity.

Package: libdsme0-dev
Section: devel
Architecture: any
Depends: libdsme0 (= ${Source-Version})
Description: Development files for dsme
 This package contains headers and static libraries needed to develop programs
 that want to communicate with the Device State Management Entity.

Package: dsme-testcases
Section: devel
Architecture: any
Depends: tbench
Description: Development files for dsme
 This package contains test cases to validate dsme's behaviour.
